<specimenCount id="9D73FD5EFFC7A707FCCBFE72A7CAC3E1" box="[857,948,428,449]" pageId="4" pageNumber="90" type="generic" typeStatus="types">two types</specimenCount>
; their presence, together with a combination of other characters, distinguish it from all similar species.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
